<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
{{template "head.gohtml" .}}
<body>
{{template "nav_new.gohtml" .}}
<main>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="main-content">
            <article class="article-detail">
                <h1 style="margin-bottom: 18px;">友情链接</h1>
                <div class="links-list">
                    {{range .friendLinks}}
                    <a class="friend-link-card" href="{{.Url}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">
                        <img class="friend-link-logo" src="{{.Logo}}" alt="{{.Name}} logo">
                        <div class="friend-link-info">
                            <div class="friend-link-title">{{.Name}}</div>
                            <div class="friend-link-desc">{{.Description}}</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    {{end}}
                </div>
                <div class="links-tips">
                    <p>欢迎优秀社区、博客、技术站点交换友链！请联系站长或在 <a href="/contact" target="_blank">联系我们</a> 页面留言。</p>
                </div>
            </article>
        </div>
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-card">
                <h3>友情链接须知</h3>
                <ul class="links-rules">
                    <li>内容健康、合法，技术/学习/社区类优先</li>
                    <li>请保持贵站可访问且有本站友链</li>
                    <li>本站保留审核与下架权利</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="sidebar-card">
                <h3>推荐社区</h3>
                <ul class="recommended-posts">
                    <li><a href="https://segmentfault.com/" target="_blank">SegmentFault 思否</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://www.v2ex.com/" target="_blank">V2EX</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://www.oschina.net/" target="_blank">开源中国</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://juejin.cn/" target="_blank">稀土掘金</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </div>
</main>
{{template "footer.gohtml" .}}
<style>
.links-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}
.friend-link-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px 22px;
    min-width: 260px;
    max-width: 420px;
    flex: 1 1 320px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-color);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
}
.friend-link-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary-color);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(25,118,210,0.08);
    background: #f5faff;
}
.friend-link-logo {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    object-fit: contain;
    margin-right: 18px;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
}
.friend-link-info {
    flex: 1;
}
.friend-link-title {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.friend-link-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-color-light);
    line-height: 1.5;
}
.links-tips {
    margin-top: 18px;
    color: var(--text-color-secondary);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--border-color);
}
.links-tips a {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-decoration: underline;
}
.links-rules {
    padding-left: 18px;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    color: var(--text-color-secondary);
    margin: 0;
}
.links-rules li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
}
@media (max-width: 900px) {
    .links-list {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 14px;
    }
    .friend-link-card {
        max-width: 100%;
    }
}
</style>
</body>
</html>